<plot>A Russian professor's world is uprooted when he makes one false step and receives news that he will be deported from the home he has grown to love- New York City. 'Hope &amp; Anchor' is the story of Konstantin's struggle to tell his daughter he must leave for Russia in a matter of days; and that his plans include her dropping everything to follow him there. Set around a poker game, the tension builds as the night barrels on, Konstantin plunging further and further into debt, his secret still remaining locked inside his chest. What Konstantin learns is that the past will never be what the future once was.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?245343</url></doc>
